🇸🇨The President of #Seychelles become the first Head of State in #Africa to take #China developed SinoPharm #COVID19 #vaccine on 10 Jan.
The statement said the Indian Ocean archipelago had received 50,000 doses of the vaccine as a donation from the United Arab Emirates #UAE 🇦🇪. https://t.co/y9nquH4s4F
